check(string,string,bool).notice: check - Checks if a build step's cache entry is still valid.

invalidate(string).notice: invalidate - Invalidates a specific cache entry by step key.

invalidateAll().notice: invalidateAll - Clears the entire build cache.

invalidateByKind(string).notice: invalidateByKind - Invalidates all cache entries whose step key contains the kind name.

invalidateBySource(string).notice: invalidateBySource - Invalidates all cache entries matching a source locator.
